Method Detail

createTempThumbnail

public java.lang.String createTempThumbnail(java.lang.String fileId)
                                     throws RPCIllegalArgumentException
Writes the thumpnail in the uploadedImages Folder with the prefix "thumb-" (defined as a constant on the file Properties.TEMPORAL_THUMB_PREXIF). Example: The fileId is "aguacate.png" the resulting temporal thumbnail will have the name "thumb-aguacate.png"

Specified by:
createTempThumbnail in interface MediaUtilRPC
Parameters:
fileId - this is the name of the image, name gived by the server as an unique id for temporal use only
Returns:
the webAddress where the image is accesible for the web application
Throws:
RPCIllegalArgumentException

organizeAndCleanFiles

public void organizeAndCleanFiles(java.lang.String tempFileId,
                                  java.lang.String DBFileName,
                                  java.lang.Integer mediaId)
                           throws RPCIllegalArgumentException
Takes the temporal image and moves it to the ORIGINAL IMAGES folder., removes the thumbnail and the temporal full size image. Creates the THUMB and BIG images, and ordered in the day's folder

Specified by:
organizeAndCleanFiles in interface MediaUtilRPC
Parameters:
tempFileId - unique temporal identifier of the image
DBFileName - the name of the file with its extension
mediaId - Data Base media Identifier
Throws:
RPCIllegalArgumentException
